data.description: Charming 2-story traditional on a large lot beckons you home to Moss bluff. Boasting a fully renovated kitchen, this home has luxury vinyl plank in living areas and bedrooms. Primary bedroom is on the first floor, and two bedrooms and full bath are upstairs. Two great details: the home features a generator and an upstairs laundry chute! Flood zone X (that's the good one!) Slab in backyard was previous shops/storage. All measurements are more or less.
